Program: The Documentary
Title: 10/03/2010
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p006hrrd
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 14 Mar 2010
Marriage websites are springing up all over the world, but nowhere more so than in India. Shaadi.com is the biggest such site in the world and more and more urban Indians are meeting their life partners online. But is online dating and marriage making changing the way Indians meet their life partners? Rajini Vaidyanathan investigates. Show less